[MEDIA PATNER: Impact Circle 5.0 by AIESEC in UNJ]

ARE YOU READY TO LEVEL UP YOUR HOBBY AND TURN IT INTO MONEY?

We present to you, Impact Circle 5.0 by AIESEC in UNJ in collaboration with Allo Bank x InvestasiKu, “Get Funds From The Fun.” 

Impact Circle 5.0 is a virtual event to raise awareness about why youth should start to maximize their hobby as a source of income. There are lots of youths who want to find a way to earn money but still unsure how. For this reason, we’ll provide you the updated insights from our amazing speakers on how to maximize your hobby and utilize the social media platform as a step to embrace your potential.

Every session will be delivered by our amazing speakers!
📌Firman Marihot, Group Head of InvestasiKu
📌 Easter Tobing, Head of Partnership, Business, and Growth Allo Bank
📌 Saskia Nandina, CEO of Vintage House

Mark your calendar! 
🗓️ Friday, October 21, 2022
⏰ 18.30 - Finish (GMT +7)
📍 Zoom Meeting
💰 FREE!

What will you get?
- Exclusive material
- E-Certificates from AlESEC & Allo Bank
- Voucher CT Corp @50k from InvestasiKu
- Allo Prime 25.000 points
- Sweater giveaway from @vintagehouse_id
- Stock investment from Investasiku

Don’t let this opportunity slips away! 
🙋🏼‍♀️ Secure your seat: aiesec.or.id/impact-circle
💁🏼‍♀️ Check our booklet for more info: bit.ly/BookletIC5_AIESECinUNJ
